# Gateway Wire Protocol

The UI communicates with the C gateway over WebSocket using a JSON-RPC style protocol.

## Envelope Format

Request: `{ "method": "noun.verb", "id": "uuid", ...params }`
Response: `{ "id": "uuid", ...result }` or `{ "id": "uuid", "error": "message" }`

## Method Naming

All methods follow `noun.verb` convention (e.g., `chat.send`, `sessions.list`).

